# рџ”Ө Key principles (donвЂ™t violate these)

### вњ… 1. Single source of truth

```text
electron/src = REAL backend
server/ = reference only
```

---

### вњ… 2. No TS in runtime

```text
Electron runs JS в†’ electron/dist
```

---

### вњ… 3. IPC layer separated

```text
electron/src/ipc/*
```

рџ‘‰ DonвЂ™t mix IPC + logic

---

### вњ… 4. main.js is thin

```text
main.js = wiring only (no business logic)
```

